Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: biliass
Version: 1.3.3
Summary: 将 B 站 XML 弹幕转换为 ASS 弹幕
Home-page: https://github.com/ShigureLab/biliass
Author: m13253, Nyakku Shigure
License: GPLv3
Description: # biliass
        
        Danmaku2ASS 的 bilili 与 yutto 适配版
        
        原版：<https://github.com/m13253/danmaku2ass>
        
        支持 XML 弹幕和 Protobuf 弹幕
        
        # Install
        
        ```bash
        pip install biliass
        ```
        
        # Usage
        
        ```bash
        # XML 弹幕
        biliass danmaku.xml -s 1920x1080 -o danmaku.ass
        # protobuf 弹幕
        biliass danmaku.protobuf -s 1920x1080 -f protobuf -o danmaku.ass
        ```
        
        ```python
        from biliass import Danmaku2ASS
        
        # xml
        Danmaku2ASS(
            xml_text_or_bytes,
            width,
            height,
            input_format="xml",
            reserve_blank=0,
            font_face="sans-serif",
            font_size=width / 40,
            text_opacity=0.8,
            duration_marquee=15.0,
            duration_still=10.0,
            comment_filter=None,
            is_reduce_comments=False,
            progress_callback=None,
        )
        
        # protobuf
        Danmaku2ASS(
            protobuf_bytes, # only bytes
            width,
            height,
            input_format="protobuf",
            reserve_blank=0,
            font_face="sans-serif",
            font_size=width / 40,
            text_opacity=0.8,
            duration_marquee=15.0,
            duration_still=10.0,
            comment_filter=None,
            is_reduce_comments=False,
            progress_callback=None,
        )
        ```
        
